---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | CyberBros Security - PDPA Compliant Data Protection"
  description="CyberBros Security privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal data in compliance with Malaysian PDPA 2010."
  keywords="privacy policy, data protection, PDPA Malaysia, personal data, cybersecurity privacy"
>
  <Navigation />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-950 via-gray-900 to-black pt-32 pb-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400">Last Updated: October 31, 2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="bg-black py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-invert prose-indigo">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-950 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 space-y-8 text-gray-300">
        
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            CyberBros Security ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your personal data and privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website <span class="text-indigo-400">cyberbrosecurity.work</span> and use our services.
          </p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">
            This policy is designed to comply with the <strong class="text-white">Personal Data Protection Act 2010 (PDPA)</strong> of Malaysia and other applicable data protection laws.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Information We Collect -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-3 mt-6">2.1 Personal Data You Provide</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">When you contact us through our website, we collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mt-3">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Name:</strong> To identify and address you properly</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Email Address:</strong> To respond to your inquiries</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Institution/Organization:</strong> To understand your context (optional)</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Message Content:</strong> To understand and respond to your inquiry</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-3 mt-6">2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">When you visit our website, we may automatically collect:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mt-3">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, device information</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent, referring websites</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Cookies:</strong> Small data files stored on your device (see Cookie Policy below)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- How We Use Your Information -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mt-3">
            <li>To respond to your inquiries and provide customer support</li>
            <li>To send information about our cybersecurity training services</li>
            <li>To improve our website and services</li>
            <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
            <li>To prevent fraud and ensure security</li>
            <li>To analyze website usage and optimize user experience</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">
            <strong class="text-white">Legal Basis:</strong> We process your personal data based on your consent, contractual necessity, legal obligations, and our legitimate business interests.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Data Sharing and Disclosure -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">4. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">We do not sell your personal data. We may share your information with:</p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-3 mt-6">4.1 Service Providers</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mt-3">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Email Service Provider (Resend):</strong> To send and receive emails</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Hosting Provider (Cloudflare):</strong> To host and deliver our website</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4 text-yellow-400 bg-yellow-900/20 border border-yellow-700/30 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è International Data Transfer:</strong> Some service providers may process data outside Malaysia. We ensure they provide adequate data protection through contractual safeguards.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-3 mt-6">4.2 Legal Requirements</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">We may disclose your information if required by law or to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mt-3">
            <li>Comply with legal processes or government requests</li>
            <li>Enforce our terms and conditions</li>
            <li>Protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property</li>
            <li>Investigate potential violations or fraud</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Data Retention -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mt-3">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Contact Form Data:</strong> Up to 2 years from last contact</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Email Communications:</strong> Up to 2 years for business records</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Analytics Data:</strong> Anonymized after 26 months</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">
            After the retention period, we will securely delete or anonymize your personal data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Your Rights Under PDPA -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">6. Your Rights Under PDPA</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">Under Malaysian PDPA 2010, you have the following rights:</p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4 mt-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-2">üîç Right to Access</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Request access to your personal data we hold</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-2">‚úèÔ∏è Right to Correction</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-2">üö´ Right to Withdraw Consent</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Withdraw your consent for data processing at any time</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-2">üóëÔ∏è Right to Data Portability</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Request your data in a structured, commonly used format</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-2">‚öñÔ∏è Right to Complain</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Lodge a complaint with the Personal Data Protection Commissioner</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-6">
            To exercise these rights, contact us at: <a href="mailto:contact@cyberbrosecurity.work" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300">contact@cyberbrosecurity.work</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Cookie Policy -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">7. Cookie Policy</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Our website uses cookies to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies are small text files stored on your device.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-3 mt-6">Types of Cookies We Use:</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-3 mt-4">
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">üîß Essential Cookies (Required)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Necessary for website functionality and security. Cannot be disabled.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">üìä Analytics Cookies (Optional)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Help us understand how visitors use our website to improve user experience.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">‚öôÔ∏è Preference Cookies (Optional)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Remember your preferences and settings for future visits.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">
            You can manage cookie preferences through the banner displayed on your first visit or through your browser settings.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Data Security -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">8. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mt-3">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Encryption:</strong> HTTPS/TLS encryption for data transmission</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Access Controls:</strong> Restricted access to personal data</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Secure Storage:</strong> Data stored on secure servers</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Regular Security Audits:</strong> Ongoing security assessments</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">
            However, no internet transmission is completely secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security but strive to use industry-standard practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Third-Party Links -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">9. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Our website may contain links to third-party websites (e.g., social media platforms). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites. Please review their privacy policies before providing any personal data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Children's Privacy -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">10. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Our services are not directed to individuals under 18 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children. If you believe we have collected data from a child, please contact us immediately.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Changes to This Policy -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">11. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of significant changes by:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4 mt-3">
            <li>Posting the updated policy on our website</li>
            <li>Updating the "Last Updated" date at the top</li>
            <li>Sending email notifications for material changes (if applicable)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-4">
            We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">12. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            If you have questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please contact us:
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-indigo-900/20 border border-indigo-700/30 p-6 rounded-lg mt-4">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-4">CyberBros Security</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li><strong class="text-white">Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@cyberbrosecurity.work" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300">contact@cyberbrosecurity.work</a></li>
              <li><strong class="text-white">Location:</strong> Malaysia</li>
              <li><strong class="text-white">Response Time:</strong> We aim to respond within 5 business days</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <p class="leading-relaxed mt-6 text-sm text-gray-400">
            For complaints related to personal data protection, you may also contact the Personal Data Protection Commissioner of Malaysia at: <a href="https://www.pdp.gov.my" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300">www.pdp.gov.my</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Consent -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900/20 to-purple-900/20 border border-indigo-700/30 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">13. Your Consent</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            By using our website and services, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with this policy, please do not use our website or services.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</MainLayout>
